snippet.title: Diana and Roma playing Police
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma pretend to play the Police. Diana is a policeman, and brother Roma is a lawbreaker. Children have fun, play together, and learn the profession of a policeman.
Subscribe to Kids Diana Show - http://bit.ly/2k7NrSx
